  "title": "Marine Surveyor",
  "description": "<p>Polytechnic Diploma In Nautical Studies or any technical diploma</p><p>On-the-Job Training Provided</p><p>Good Management Reporting & Writing Reports Skills</p><p>Able to Align with the Marine Operational Nature of Work, Which Involves Going On Board the Vessels and Being Available for Work on a 24/7 Basis When Required.</p><p>Type of Hours Worked Will Be Paid Accordingly<br /></p><p>Assist In Conducting Marine Surveys and Inspections, Including Vessel Condition Assessments, Cargo inspections, and Safety Audits.</p><p>Maintain Proper Documentation of Survey Findings in the Head Office</p><p>Ability to Work Cross-Functionality On Board Vessels As Assigned by Senior Marine Surveyor / Manager.</p>",
